title: *FIRST MONTH OF RENT FREE* Stylish South Austin Living *NEST included*
posting_body: ['* First full month is completely free, this unit has a prorated rent of $1,335 and has a waived deposit with approved credit!', '*', 'Check out this Modern apartment in the heart of South Austin!', 'Boasting walkability to the South Park Meadows shopping center and easy access to I35 to get you downtown in less than 10 minutes!', 'With two separate dog parks, your four-legged friends will get the exercise it needs.', 'Hosting a large hangout pool and a separate lap pool, you can stay cool in the hot months.', 'They make it easy to love your apartment with a fully equipped, gourmet kitchen, granite countertops with tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, in-home washer & dryer and 9 foot ceilings with open floor plans.', '**They also have 2/2 available starting at $1,155**', "Don't miss out on this great special, call me today to find out more!", 'Trent Guerra', 'Apartment Locator + Sales Manager', 'Apartment Hunters LLC', '(8 1 7) 9 9 9-8 8 2 9', "** As a full-time apartment locator I will work day and night to help you find the perfect apartment here in the beautiful Austin Tx, my service is completely FREE to you so please don't hesitate and call me today!", 'Check out our Apartment Hunters Facebook and Google pages to see over one hundred 5 star reviews written from past clients and their experience with me!', '**']
